{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fill","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Napravite prilagodljiva podešavanja koristeći auto-fill","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija za ponavljanje ima opciju nazvanu <dfn>auto-fill</dfn>. Ovo vam omogućava automatsko unosenje više redova ili kolona veličine koje želite, koliko prostor kontejner dozvoljava. Možete kreirati dinamička podešavanja kombinujući <code>auto-fill</code> i <code>minmax</code>, kao što je prikazano:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">repeat(auto-fill, minmax(60px, 1fr));\n</code></pre>\n<p>Kada kontajner menja veličinu, ovaj raspored nastavlja da ubacuje kolone od 60px i širi ih dok ne može da stane više. <strong>Napomena:</strong> Ako vaš kontajner ne može da smesti sve elemente na jednoj liniji (redu), prebaciće ih dole u novi red.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a94fe5469fb03452672e461","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>U prvoj mreži, koristite <code>auto-fill</code> i <code>repeat</code> da popunite mrežu kolonama širine minimalnog nivoa <code>60px</code> i maksimalnog nivoa <code>1fr</code>. Zatim promenite veličinu prikaza da biste videli kako funkcioniše auto-fill.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/cmzdycW","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301126,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fill"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n  .item5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 100px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(60px, 1fr));\r\n\r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container2 {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 100px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: Silver;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(60px, 1fr));\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container2\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Darasa la <code>container</code> bi trebalo da ima svojstvo <code>grid-template-columns</code> koje sadrži <code>repeat</code> i <code>auto-fill</code>, koji će popuniti mreže i kolone sa širinom od minimalne vrednosti <code>60px</code> do maksimalne vrednosti <code>1fr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  code,\r\n  /.container\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-template-columns\\s*?:\\s*?repeat\\s*?\\(\\s*?auto-fill\\s*?,\\s*?minmax\\s*?\\(\\s*?60px\\s*?,\\s*?1fr\\s*?\\)\\s*?\\)\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fill","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fit","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/limit-item-size-using-the-minmax-function","id":"5a94fe5469fb03452672e461","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n  }\r\n</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-flexible-layouts-using-auto-fill"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}